 * PURPOSE
 * - Reads one Homework Completions record.
 * - Reads the linked Enrollment record.
 * - Reads the linked Homework curriculum record.
 * - Reads all linked Submission Assets.
 * - Builds a branded parent homework feedback email.
 * - Sends the email payload to Make.com.
 * - Writes back final send status to Homework Completions.
 *
 * CURRENT AIRTABLE SETUP
 * - Automation Name:
 *   071 - Email, Notifications, and External Handoffs - Send Homework Feedback Email Webhook
 *
 * - Folder:
 *   07 - Email, Notifications, and External Handoffs
 *
 * - Trigger Type:
 *   When record matches conditions
 *
 * - Trigger Table:
 *   Homework Completions
 *
 * - Trigger Conditions:
 *   Parent Feedback Ready? is checked
 *   Parent Feedback Sent? is not checked
 *   Satisfactory? is checked
 *   Coach Feedback is not empty
 *   Enrollment is not empty
 *   Homework is not empty
 *   Submission Assets is not empty
 *
 * REQUIRED INPUT VARIABLES
 * - recordId
 * - makeWebhookUrl
 * - sendMode
 * - testRecipientEmail
 *
 * OPTIONAL INPUT VARIABLES
 * - replyTo
 *
 * IMPORTANT LIVE/TEST RULE
 * - Test mode sends to testRecipientEmail only.
 * - Test mode does NOT check Parent Feedback Sent?.
